title: VA Indie Electro Rock October 2013 - Just A Touch (Dutch Treat I
description:
Already the fourth playlist of the Indie Playlists October 2013. A Nice list, but for me one of the hardest until now. 30 good tracks, all very different. So it was hard to make it flow. So this list will undergo probably some changes before it is included in the collection definitely. In the mean while.... Enjoy,
